<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>ạbrạhym srkys</author>
<title>bạsm ạlmsyḥ njtmʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- biạs̊mi ạl̊masīḥi naj̊tamiʿ̊
 fāi̹nãhu ạl̊fādī ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 yah̊wah yasūʿu ạl̊mur̊tafiʿ̊
 wah̊wa ạlrãyỉysu min̊ qadīm̊

[V2]
 2- fālậbu qad̊ ạảqāmahu
 mukẖalĩṣaⁿạ warayĩsā
 wakulũ sul̊ṭāni ạlsãmā
 wālạ̉r̊ḍi lahu muṭ̊laqā

[V3]
 3- fah̊wa ại̹dẖaⁿạ rā̊̉suⁿ lanā
 fī was̊ṭinā kamā waʿad̊
 hūa hūa ạảm̊saⁿạ kadẖā
 wāl̊yaẘma wāi̹lay̱ ạlạ̉bad̊

[V4]
 4- biạs̊mi ạảbīhi yukẖ̊biru
 fī was̊ṭinā yusabĩḥu
 bisẖakẖ̊ṣihi naf̊takẖiru
 wabihi ạảẙḍaⁿạ naf̊raḥu

[V5]
 5- wālrũwḥu ạảẙḍaⁿạ yā̊̉kẖudẖu
 mimãạ lahu wayukẖ̊biru
 jamālahu yub̊dī lanā
 maj̊dahu ạảẙḍaⁿạ yuẓ̊hiru

[V6]
 6- fal̊nuʿ̊ṭi kulũnā ại̹dẖaⁿạ
 lahu maqāmaⁿạ sāmīā
 wal̊nan̊taẓir̊ biṭāʿaẗiⁿ
 ʿaẘnaⁿạ warusẖ̊daⁿạ kāmilạ

[V7]
 7- fayā lagẖib̊ṭaẗiⁿ lanā
 ại̹dẖi ạl̊masīḥu rā̊̉sunā
 hadẖā hūa ạm̊tīāzunā
 ʿani ạlsẖũʿūbi ḥaẘlanā</lyrics>
</song>